{"tid":1959043,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"美國在台協會臉書貼文　挺台加入世衛大會","createTime":"2020-04-05T06:42:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-05T06:58:41.000Z","uid":28114,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3e5348d0796990cc843bbf9321799e01ccecfb12","tid":1959043,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T06:42:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20200404/640_262bb39ac608ff5f59fc86ca8ed41e4e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20200404%2F640_262bb39ac608ff5f59fc86ca8ed41e4e.jpg&h=4201fa62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n翻攝美國在台協會臉書<br />\n<br />\n美國在台協會今在臉書貼文，力挺台灣加入世界衛生大會，貼文引述美國國務院東亞暨太平洋事務局（EAP）的推特發文，內容寫道：「台灣在預防新冠肺炎傳播方面居世界領導地位，美國與台灣皆期盼與全球國家分享 #台灣模式。台灣在全球衛生領域扮演要角，應恢復台灣在世界衛生大會的觀察員身分。」<br />\n<br />\n美國國務院已在3日發新聞稿稱，美台官員上月31日舉行視訊論壇，討論台灣對抗疫情的台灣模式，會議也談及台灣恢復世衛大會觀察員的努力。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）      <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/politics/20200404/YKZRHZGKXWOUVUGERBW7FENTBU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fpolitics%2F20200404%2FYKZRHZGKXWOUVUGERBW7FENTBU%2F&d=4DrNtUYtvprXc3sGeUgfzxAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=25ed8233\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fpolitics%2F20200404%2FYKZRHZGKXWOUVUGERBW7FENTBU%2F&h=f3b53e57\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/politics/20200404/YKZRHZGKXWOUVUGERBW7FENTBU/</a>"},{"pid":"316582d11c115bdf38f07d1b57bacb94cf6a498f","tid":1959043,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T06:47:45.000Z","msg":"邱騰華出嚟未"},{"pid":"fbaf4bdd3433fc1cd94147e49ca23e92b474c84c","tid":1959043,"uid":301479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T06:54:45.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c0e0f8b85ee0f7b224dbe167592a74ed69a757a9","tid":1959043,"uid":301479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T06:54:55.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a06cd48a0a1bdf5c31226c20f919aada7e7d6d24","tid":1959043,"uid":63029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T06:58:41.000Z","msg":"一齊退出，另立國際衛生組織好過啦<br />\n<br />\n篩走晒啲奶共國"}]}